(1697, 661, 'case_strategy', 'We worked with management to establish and implement several turnaround initiatives including (i) the renewed focus on new business efforts and personnel, (ii) the implementation of a Risk Prevention Program and (iii) the further implementation of technology-based improvements. Historically, HSS has demonstrated an ability to grow strategically in existing and new markets. As such, we worked with HSS to help them grow through the “build then staff” model as opposed to the “staff then build” model, which can be a significant drag on profitability. '),
(1698, 661, '_case_strategy', 'field_52387b3915786'),
