(142, 1, '2013-09-23 16:09:37', '2013-09-23 16:09:37', '<p>Blake Goddard, an Associate at Caymus Equity, is actively involved in all of the firm’s activities, focusing on evaluation and selection of private equity investments, financial modeling, transaction due diligence and providing strategic and operational assistance to current portfolio companies. <o:p></o:p></p><p>Prior to joining Caymus Equity in 2016, Blake was an Analyst at ING Capital LLC, working in the Acquisition Finance Group, where he was focused on leveraged buyout transactions and ABL credit facilities for financial sponsor clients.<o:p></o:p></p>', 'Blake E. Goddard', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'blake-goddard', '', '', '2016-11-15 17:57:53', '2016-11-15 17:57:53', '', 0, 'http://caymuspartners.com/wordpress/?post_type=our_team&#038;p=142', 0, 'our_team', '', 0),
