(145, 1, '2013-09-23 16:13:56', '2013-09-23 16:13:56', '<p>Blake Cummings, an Associate at Caymus Equity, is active in all aspects of the firm’s activities, with a focus on evaluation and selection of new investment opportunities, financial modeling, transaction due diligence and assisting with the strategic and operational management of current portfolio companies. <o:p></o:p></p><p>Prior to joining Caymus Equity, Blake worked on the Mergers &amp; Acquisitions team at Consolidated Container Company, a portfolio company of Bain Capital, where he was responsible for acquiring and integrating target companies, establishing joint ventures, and executing the company’s growth strategies. Previously, Blake was a Senior Analyst at Founders Investment Bank, a boutique merchant banking firm focused on merger &amp; acquisition advisory and niche direct investing.</p>', 'Blake A. Cummings', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'blake-cummings', '', '', '2016-11-15 17:57:13', '2016-11-15 17:57:13', '', 0, 'http://caymuspartners.com/wordpress/?post_type=our_team&#038;p=145', 0, 'our_team', '', 0),
