(326, 1, '2013-10-11 20:05:42', '2013-10-11 20:05:42', '<p>David Chan, a Senior Associate of Caymus Equity, has significant private equity, operating, restructuring, and financial advisory experience focused on the lower middle market. Mr. Chan is active in all aspects of the firm’s activities, with a particular focus on new investment origination and execution. During his tenure at Caymus Partners, Mr. Chan assisted lower middle market companies in executing transactions through private placements, acquisitions, and divestitures, representing over $100 million in transaction value.</p>\n\n<p>In 2010, Mr. Chan co-founded and invested in an online e-commerce company and served as the project manager, responsible for operating and growing the company to a $20 million run-rate in annual revenue with 35 employees within nine months of inception. The company was recognized by the Technology Association of Georgia (TAG) as one of the top ten innovative technology companies in Georgia in 2009.</p>', 'David K. Chan', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '145-autosave-v1', '', '', '2013-10-11 20:05:42', '2013-10-11 20:05:42', '', 145, 'http://caymuspartners.com/wordpress/index.php/145-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(330, 1, '2013-10-22 17:08:34', '2013-10-22 17:08:34', '<li class="span3">\r\n             <div class="thumbnail">\r\n                <img src="<?php bloginfo(\'template_directory\'); ?>/img/img001b.jpg">\r\n                <div class="caption">\r\n                  <h3>What We Look For</h3>\r\n                  <p>We seek to partner with privately-held, profitable companies to provide capital, operating experience and leadership, enabling them to grow and transition.</p>\r\n                  <a class="read-more" href="/index.php/what-we-look-for">Read More</a>\r\n                </div>\r\n             </div>\r\n        </li>     \r\n        <li class="span3">\r\n             <div class="thumbnail">\r\n                <img src="<?php bloginfo(\'template_directory\'); ?>/img/img002.jpg">\r\n                <div class="caption">\r\n                  <h3>Our Team</h3>\r\n                  <p>Over 100 years of collective investing and operating experience, including over 40 years in starting, acquiring, operating, growing and successfully exiting a variety of businesses.</p>\r\n                  <a class="read-more" href="/index.php/our-team/">Read More</a>\r\n                </div>\r\n             </div>\r\n         </li>\r\n         <li class="span3">\r\n             <div class="thumbnail">\r\n                <img src="<?php bloginfo(\'template_directory\'); ?>/img/img003.jpg">\r\n                <div class="caption">\r\n                  <h3>Our Portfolio</h3>\r\n                  <p>We invest in collaboration with superior management and work closely with our partners to support their efforts to grow, build market share and streamline operations.</p>\r\n                  <a class="read-more" href="/index.php/portfolio">Read More</a>\r\n                </div>\r\n             </div>\r\n         </li>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '299-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-10-22 17:08:34', '2013-10-22 17:08:34', '', 299, 'http://caymusequity.com/index.php/299-