(570, 2, '2013-09-23 16:05:20', '2013-09-23 16:05:20', '<p>Nancy Faux is the firm’s Chief Financial Officer and is responsible for managing Caymus Equity’s funds administration. She oversees finance and administration, human resources, information technology and investor relations. Nancy’s responsibilities include financial reporting and portfolio monitoring. She works closely with the investment professionals to report on the company and financial performance to the limited partners.</p><div><p>Prior to joining Caymus Equity, Nancy was the Chief Financial Officer at High Meadows School. Previously, Nancy worked at The Westminster Schools as the Assistant Director of Facilities. Prior to those positions, she was a Vice President at Citibank, N. A. in their Foreign Exchange Trading Department and Corporate Finance Department. Nancy is a Certified Public Accountant.</p></div>', 'Nancy S. Faux', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'nancy-s.-faux', '', '', '2016-11-15 17:58:33', '2016-11-15 17:58:33', '', 0, 'http://caymusequity.com/?post_type=our_team&#038;p=570', 0, 'our_team', '', 0),
