(583, 2, '2015-04-23 17:43:41', '2015-04-23 17:43:41', '<p>We seek to partner with excellent entrepreneurial management teams that are believed to be of high integrity and who have a compelling business strategy, a well-developed framework for implementing their strategy, a sustainable and scalable business model and platform, extensive industry and operating experience, and an established record of performance.</p>\r\n<h5>Industry Focus</h5>\r\n<div class="row" id="industry-focus">\r\n <span class="span3"><span class="span3">\r\n    </span></span><h5><img src="<?php bloginfo(\'template_directory\'); ?>/img/icon_business.gif" />Business Services</h5><span class="span3"><span class="span3">\r\n    </span></span><p>Service providers that leverage technology, information assets or a unique business process or strategy to deliver value to their customers.</p><span class="span3">\r\n </span>\r\n <span class="span3"><span class="span3">\r\n    </span></span><h5><img src="<?php bloginfo(\'template_directory\'); ?>/img/icon_health.jpg" />Healthcare Services</h5><span class="span3"><span class="span3">\r\n    </span></span><p>Healthcare services companies with an established customer base and a scalable business. We avoid medical devices and biotechnology.</p><span class="span3">\r\n </span>\r\n <span class="span3"><span class="span3">\r\n    </span></span><h5><img src="<?php bloginfo(\'template_directory\'); ?>/img/icon_consumer.jpg" />Consumer</h5><span class="span3"><span class="span3">\r\n    </span></span><p>Manufacturers of consumer oriented products and consumer services companies that compete in markets that are well established and not typically subject to the risks associated with economic cycles and technological obsolescence.</p><span class="span3">\r\n </span>\r\n <span class="span3"><span class="span3">\r\n    </span></span><h5><img src="<?php bloginfo(\'template_directory\'); ?>/img/icon_niche.jpg" />Niche Manufacturing</h5><span class="span3"><span class="span3">\r\n    </span></span><p>Manufacturers that develop or reposition products and services in a way that adds value to a distinct customer base.</p><span class="span3">\r\n </span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row" id="industry-focus-2">\r\n<span class="span6 text"><span class="span6 text">\r\n</span></span><h5>Financial Criteria:</h5><span class="span6 text"><span class="span6 text">\r\n</span></span><ul>\r\n    <li>Targeted valuation of $10 million to $50 million</li>\r\n    <li>Revenue: $10 million to $100 million</li>\r\n    <li>EBITDA: $2 million to $10 million</li>\r\n    <li>Strong free cash flow</li>\r\n</ul><span class="span6 text"><span class="span6 text">\r\n</span></span><h5>Prospect for Value Creation:</h5><span class="span6 text"><span class="span6 text">\r\n</span></span><ul>\r\n    <li>Organic growth</li>\r\n    <li>Ability to access new markets</li>\r\n    <li>Ability to broaden product or service offerings</li>\r\n    <li>Strategic acquisitions</li>\r\n</ul><span class="span6 text"><span class="span6 text">\r\n</span></span><h5>Market Impact:</h5><span class="span6 text"><span class="span6 text">\r\n</span></span><ul>\r\n    <li>Differentiated or proprietary product, service, distribution channel,\r\n process, or technology</li>\r\n    <li>Meaningful cost advantage and/or high switching costs</li>\r\n    <li>Strong customer base</li>\r\n    <li>High barriers to entry</li>\r\n</ul><span class="span6 text"><span class="span6 text">\r\n</span></span><h5>Management:</h5><span class="span6 text"><span class="span6 text">\r\n</span></span><p>Strong management teams interested in partnering with Caymus Equity post-transaction, to take their companies to the next level</p><span class="span6 text">\r\n</span>\r\n<span class="span6 image">\r\n <img src="<?php bloginfo(\'template_directory\'); ?>/img/lookfor_img.jpg" />\r\n</span>\r\n</div>', 'What We Look For', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '6-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-04-23 17:43:41', '2015-04-23 17